{"tid":1246824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣的最大敵人是免費報紙","createTime":"2019-06-21T01:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T02:09:55.000Z","uid":59869,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"67b24f582435f42caa00778a0e7776e8cb482b07","tid":1246824,"uid":59869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"朝朝早屋企同office樓下都一大班廢老排隊拎免費報紙<br />\n而家連大公都有派免費版去各大屋苑<br />\n呢d報紙平時講乜唱乜大家心中有數<br />\n班廢老耳濡目染有晒成見<br />\n唔係整一兩張長輩圖就可以改變<br />\n<br />\n所以係文宣輿論方面我地最好都係採取分化策略<br />\n係建制同政府之間下手去&quot;改正&quot;某些觀點<br />\n例如&quot;建制派支持應為警察伸張正義&quot;再接&quot;支持成獨立調查委員會&quot;呢d<br />\n<br />\n選舉方面，呢班廢老一定唔會投非建制架啦<br />\n快d登記做選民啦"},{"pid":"80e009b38b5256caef181bed10930ad2fedce121","tid":1246824,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:40:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今次肯定得：我岩岩po左信上美國大媒體Buzzfeed，麻煩入link留comment同share去！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.buzzfeed.com/hongkongkidsaredying/hong-kong-citizens-need-your-help-emf7dtv2y2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeed.com%2Fhongkongkidsaredying%2Fhong-kong-citizens-need-your-help-emf7dtv2y2&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=8de30f94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.buzzfeed.com/hongkongkidsaredying/hong-kong-citizens-need-your-help-emf7dtv2y2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個新post（請順便幫我推，我第三晚通頂，跪求可憐我）<br />\n[急！一定有國際傳媒留意] 出左反送中post係國際知名媒體，求大家入link留comment同share<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1246617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1246617</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[終於有信比大家!] 請廣傳 唔好再比林鄭 黑警 醫管局fake 9外國傳媒，心好累，我連通兩晚頂搵資訊比大家的<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244090</a><br />\n</strong></span></span></blockquote>credit to 月娥奔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a462fd641e46bbc7a64d5ba546c13dd2f3546e","tid":1246824,"uid":24168,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"大家見到有就攞，之後攞去回收<br />\n<br />\n再甚者可以組隊回收免費報，每日公佈毀滅咗幾多份免費報，自己有回收收入之餘，仲可以直接打擊佢廣告收入 (不過可能會俾黑社會搞)"},{"pid":"b86e1a08ce4471e1f0005f16e826d3c8a1c337f8","tid":1246824,"uid":14494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:49:30.000Z","msg":"支持成立獨立調查委員會，還警隊清白"},{"pid":"ef6547f8424d6f16d3f711598816baa6c29cc466","tid":1246824,"uid":61520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:49:55.000Z","msg":"香港是否得救，是否被林鄭秋後算帳，靠白宮聯署及G20請願。<br />\n白宮聯署是打響頭炮，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">簽名數字不要低得難看啊！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=7bc98657\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs</a><br />\n=====================================================<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山， 各位修行</span>"},{"pid":"07794335c73f28edd7b5d32d9546c106ce30e5f0","tid":1246824,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:59:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e22c17892d384ac4d011fa9c950aaca70ce5dfa3","tid":1246824,"uid":21002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20